<br>
Empty bottles everywhere, along with fragments of armor-must have been a celebration of rare proportions.  That no one is awake in such a perilous land is puzzling.  It may also be fatal.<br>
<br>
&quot;Duty is a mountain...&quot; being my motto, I take up the responsibility of protecting my friends while they rest.  While maintaining my unseen vigil, I think &quot;Friends!  They have not even left me the meanest dregs from the cheapest bottle.&quot;  <br>
<br>
