           Journal entry...&quot;By Brells Beard&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;  Darkness and confusion were my companions as some unseen force was batting me around like some dwarven ball.<br>
Bodies lie all around their faces contorted in fear. In most unnatural positions.  Companions I have fought with and Healed many times were being struck down and I was helpless to heal. I could feel my own life fading but was unable to move. The stench of death filled my lungs choking me. then I awoke. I wonder if there is meaning? By Brell's Beard help me.&quot;<br>
<br>
As Malfi wrote she wrinkled her nose in disgust. What was that wicked stench? &quot;Has someone killed a goblin and let it sit in the sun for three days and just now slice open it's stomach?&quot; Malfi heard a low roll of thunder in the distance.  She remarked her aching shoulder must be gettin better. Since it were about to rain and her shoulder felt normal for a change.  &quot;well there goes my barometer. &quot;  Another waft of the foul smelling atmosphere floated through her tent.  &quot;My lands that is stifiling!&quot;   Malfi pondered the origin of this sudden afront on her senses.  &quot;Someone has to much meat in their diet or a gully dwarf has found refuge in someones arse and died.&quot;  Malfi prayed herself back to sleep. &quot;Oh Brell please bring me a change in the breeze&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/felvenelitefrm5.showMessageRange?topicID=44.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b>  </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/felvenelitefrm5.showPrevMessage?topicID=44.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/felvenelitefrm5.showNextMessage?topicID=44.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/felvenelitefrm5.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=44.topic&index=31><img src=http://www.elvenelite.com/images/reply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/felvenelitefrm5.emailToFriend?topicID=44.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub140.ezboard.com/felvenelitefrm5.threadControl?topicID=44.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a h